{"type":"message","id":"0ecd5110","parentId":"581913c8","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:33.503Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1772092113487}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3e71762","parentId":"0ecd5110","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:49.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a new session. I should:\n1. Read my SOUL.md to understand who I am\n2. Read USER.md to understand who I'm helping\n3. Check for memory files (today and yesterday) if they exist\n4. Read MEMORY.md since this is a main session\n5. Then greet the user appropriately\n\nLet me start by reading these files to understand my identity and context","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-9030f4ddc974c9e5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-863196400c56d6ad","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-8afee9bd3dfa62db","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-a519e590a0af51b7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":9807,"output":283,"cacheRead":4048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14138,"cost":{"input":0.00372666,"output":0.0004811,"cacheRead":0.00076912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00497688}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772092113498}}
{"type":"message","id":"69bc7de6","parentId":"b3e71762","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:50.016Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-9030f4ddc974c9e5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772092130007}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2c91b37","parentId":"69bc7de6","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:50.034Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-863196400c56d6ad","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772092130029}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c2693ca","parentId":"d2c91b37","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:50.051Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-8afee9bd3dfa62db","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772092130042}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3b2803c","parentId":"5c2693ca","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:48:50.065Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-a519e590a0af51b7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The inventory refers to the inventory tab google sheet: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU\nThe cleaning refers to the cleaning tab of google sheet: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU\nThe lease command ALSO uses the same Google Sheet ID: 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU (Inventory, Cleaning, Rent Tracker, and Inventory Data tabs are all inside this sheet.)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772092130059}}
{"type":"message","id":"e75e7c1a","parentId":"e3b2803c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:49:16.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hey. I'm online now. Looking at the files, it seems like this is a fresh workspace — IDENTITY.md and USER.md are still blank templates, but MEMORY.md has some info about Google Sheets for inventory, cleaning, and rent tracking.\n\nThe SOUL.md gives me a good sense of what's expected — be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, and respect boundaries.\n\nSince this seems like a first session (based on BOOTSTRAP.md instructions and the blank identity files), I should greet the user and start figuring out who I am and who they are. But I need to be concise — 1-3 sentences.\n\nLet me greet them naturally and ask what they want to do, keeping it conversational.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I'm online and ready to help. What are we working on?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":10895,"output":340,"cacheRead":4048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15283,"cost":{"input":0.0041401,"output":0.0005780000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00076912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00548722}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772092130066}}
